Logs.Comment:
Sent by Will at 05:12 - Thank you for your patience while our engineers diverted power around the underground network fault area. We have now restored power to all but one of the 1366 properties affected. We're sorry for any disruption this unexpected power cut caused.

If your power isn't back on, we'd still like to keep you updated. If we aren't currently in contact with you by phone or in person at your property, please call us on 08003163105 which is free from landlines and mobiles.

We know that being without power can be especially difficult, so we're sorry for the outage. Please rest assured our staff will continue to work around the clock to keep the lights on.

Sent at 05:02 by Will - More electricity has been diverted thanks to our ground team's continued work, and the lights are now safely back on to 220 further properties.

We know that 92 properties are still without electricity. If this is the case at your property, don't worry; I'll still keep you informed.

If your electricity has come back on now, or does so at any time in the future, simply click this link to stop receiving our SMS updates: bit.ly/348KOZ3.
